data.text:
(Xinhua) 15:22, July 27, 2023

CHENGDU, July 27 (Xinhua) -- Indonesian President Joko Widodo on Thursday arrived in Chengdu, capital city of southwest China's Sichuan Province, to attend the opening ceremony of the 31st summer edition of the FISU World University Games and visit China.

(Web editor: Zhang Kaiwei, Liang Jun)
